race.comment: Very even where LITTLE BIGHORN (7) gets chance to find some winning form. Has been thereabouts in richer company lately and looks well placed here. Overdue and should go close. DIAMOND INDARUF (5) was a winner fresh then outclassed in far tougher two back. Solid latest and looks close to another win but will just need some luck from a tricky gate. SHEZASMOKEY (10) is a handy mare with ability resuming. Must have had an issue at the end of last campaign and has been in and out a couple of times but fitter for recent jump-outs and is definitely up to this level if presented on song. PRANCING QUEEN (9) is overdue and rates a leading player again.
